  return cached.route; // 30 min TTL

### 2. Error Handling
```typescript
// ‚úÖ GOOD: Retry con exponential backoff
async function fetchWithRetry(url, maxRetries = 3) {
  for (let i = 0; i < maxRetries; i++) {
    try {
      return await fetch(url);
    } catch (error) {
      if (i === maxRetries - 1) throw error;
      await sleep(Math.pow(2, i) * 1000); // 1s, 2s, 4s
    }
  }
}

// ‚úÖ GOOD: Fallback graceful
try {
  return await hereRoutingAPI();
} catch (error) {
  console.error('HERE API failed, using fallback');
  return calculateBasicRoute(); // Haversine
}
```

### 3. Performance
